                        <div class="card card-default">
                            <img class="card-img-top img-responsive" src="~/Content/StateTemplate/images/services/toLibraries/erate.jpg" alt="servers" />
                            <div class="card-block">
                                <h4 class="card-title">E-Rate and California Teleconnect Fund (CTF) Information for Libraries</h4>
                                <p>E-rate and the CTF are programs that provide discounts on broadband and telecommunications services to public libraries. Although there are differences in eligible services and discount rates, it is possible for libraries to receive significant discounts on broadband and telecommunications costs by using both E-rate and CTF discounts.</p>
                                <a href="/services/to-libraries/e-rate" class="btn btn-default">READ MORE</a>
