                            <div class="card-block">
                                <h4 class="card-title">California Library Statistics</h4>
                                <p>The State Library annually collects California Library Statistics, a compilation of statistical data from public libraries throughout the state. This data is part of a national public library data collection conducted by the Institute for Museum and Library Services, which provides comparative statistics for libraries across the country.</p>
                                <a href="/services/to-libraries/statistics" class="btn btn-default">READ MORE</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="third">
                        <div class="card card-default">
                            <img class="card-img-top img-responsive" src="~/Content/StateTemplate/images/services/toLibraries/libdir.jpg" alt="California map" />
                            <div class="card-block">
                                <h4 class="card-title">California Library Directory</h4>
                                <p>The California Library Directory is derived from California Library Statistics data, and includes location and service information for main and branch public libraries, as well as a headquarters directory and online interactive map. </p>
                                <a href="/services/to-libraries/library-directory" class="btn btn-default">READ MORE</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="group">
